Que 27) What is Dependency Injection in Angular?
-------------------------------------------------
Dependency Injection means:
üëâ Instead of creating an object inside a class,
üëâ Angular automatically provides (injects) it from outside.
If a component needs a service,
Angular gives that service automatically.
You do not need to create it using new.
‚úÖ Why We Use Dependency Injection?
1Ô∏è‚É£ To reuse code
2Ô∏è‚É£ To reduce tight coupling
3Ô∏è‚É£ To make testing easy
4Ô∏è‚É£ To manage services easily
‚úÖ Important Points (Simple)
1Ô∏è‚É£ Angular has a built-in DI system.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Services are injected through the constructor.
3Ô∏è‚É£ We use @Injectable() for services.
4Ô∏è‚É£ Angular creates and manages the object for us.









